text: Just want to say this to the  ignorant social lynch mob that   @karanjohar is a bigger victim in this context compared to their ill perceived and suddenly discovered victim Sushant

text: WITHOUT NEPOTISM SOCIETY WILL COLLAPSE BECAUSE NEPOTISM(FAMILIAL LOVE ) IS THE FUNDAMENTAL TENET OF A SOCIAL STRUCTURE..Like u shouldn‚Äôt  love others wife more, u also shouldnt love others children more

name: Ram Gopal Varma
text: Talent is never an absolute but merely a perception based on various factors like different individuals,critics,box office etc and my proof is that two days before no one in the social media was crying hoarse why Sushant is not bigger than Ranveer Singh and Ranbir Kapoor

name: Ram Gopal Varma
text: And for all the hue and cry about the super talent being suppressed I will take a bet that 48 hours before now for many many months there wasn‚Äôt a single social media comment demanding to see Sushant from all the millions who are now blaming @karanjohar  for not showing him

name: Ram Gopal Varma
text: Will any of the umpteen @karanjohar hating social media warriors chose anybody outside beyond their friends and families ??? It‚Äôs fundamental human nature to do only for the near and dear ones

name: Ram Gopal Varma
text: Nepotism spoken in a negative context is a joke because entire society is based on only a family loving concept ..Should @iamsrk launch someone unknown instead of Aryan just because someone is more talented (in whose view is the point?)

name: Ram Gopal Varma
text: Of the people who are venomously targeting @karanjohar partly they are outright ignorant of how things work in film industry and partly they  hate his success and are just taking advantage of poor Sushanth‚Äôs  death to vent their suppressed jealousy towards @karanjohar

name: Ram Gopal Varma
text: There‚Äôs no such thing as insiders and outsiders and it‚Äôs only  audience who decide who they like and dont ..Film families however big they are can never have power to influence the audience and also don‚Äôt forget that @karanjohar is becos people made him big and not himself

name: Ram Gopal Varma
text: And if Sushant hung on ,then in about 15 or 20 years he would have become an insider when he‚Äôs launching his own son and some outsider Prashant would have blamed him like how everyone now is blaming @Karanjohar

name: Ram Gopal Varma
text: And for all the sound being made on social media about the super talented guy being sidelined the truth is it‚Äôs the people who are watching the other actors more than sushant and @Karanjohar couldn‚Äôt be holding a gun to the audiences head

name: Ram Gopal Varma
text: Bollywood is hard place becos people want to jump to grab stars and higher they jump the harder they are likely to fall .Sushant atleast grabbed the moon , but what about umpteen others who dint take off from ground  ..Are they supposed to kill themselves blaming the universe?

name: Ram Gopal Varma
text: No matter how many supposedly conspired to drive Sushant out (For what reason I can‚Äôt fathom when he can make money for them ) there were umpteen others wanting to work with him. ..But like it was his choice not to do with them,it‚Äôs the others choice not to work with him

name: Ram Gopal Varma
text: Also all insiders of Bollywood were sometimes outsiders starting from @SrBachchan onwards ..@karanjohar is up there not because he is an insider but because his films are seen by millions ..We all know as much failures coming from film families as much as from outside

name: Ram Gopal Varma
text: If Sushant after 12 yrs of fame and money took his life becos he was made to feel like an outsider then a 100 actors suicides per day will be justified who couldn‚Äôt reach anywhere near Sushant. If u can‚Äôt b happy with what u have u will never be happy with whatever u have.Period!

name: Ram Gopal Varma
text: Blaming @karanjohar for what happened is ridiculous and just shows lack of understanding of how film industry works ..Even assuming Karan had a problem with Sushant it‚Äôs his choice of who he wants to work with,like its any film makers choice about who they want to work with

name: Ram Gopal Varma
text: How politicians like Mulayam,Uddhav etc give sons, relatives first preference ,Like how Dhirubhai will give all his monies to Mukesh ,Anil ,Like how all families will give their own families first preference similarly Bollywood families do same ..So where‚Äôs nepotism not there  ?

name: Ram Gopal Varma
text: A most important point of the criminal justice system is to prove the guilt of criminals through a due process of law ..if we start giving punishments based on police claims,media speculations and uninformed people‚Äôs outcries society will collapse

name: Ram Gopal Varma
text: The urgency is to capture them so that they won‚Äôt cause further crime which the police did ..But when they are already in custody by fast tracking punishment,the entire system will lose out on the insights of the crime forever

name: Ram Gopal Varma
text: The purpose of due process of law  is to find the entire details of the crime in terms of both the failure of the system and the degree of who‚Äôs more responsible so that it can be used for the future in crime prevention

name: Ram Gopal Varma
text: The outrage in the people might be justified considering the brutality of the crime but the police themselves taking law into their own hands and killing will amount to nothing but disregarding the judiciary and paving way for a barbaric police state society

name: Ram Gopal Varma
text: The point of a criminal justice system in any civilised society is that police will arrest,investigate  and furnish evidence to the judiciary which will study the veracity of the facts and then decide on the quantum of punishment .

name: Ram Gopal Varma
text: With regard to encounter killings ,the fundamental foundation of any society is to control emotional outbursts and apply rationality in a due process of the rule of law ..so encounters cannot be justified under any circumstances

name: Ram Gopal Varma
text: An interview I did on RAPE https://t.co/w5Gk90wU5I

name: Ram Gopal Varma
text: Fear of punishment can never stop any crime because a criminal by nature will believe that he will never be caught ..if he even thinks he might get caught he will never commit a crime

name: Ram Gopal Varma
text: Instead of just catching,punishing and forgetting till the next rape happens we as people should hear from their mouths why exactly they came to think of women like prey to be hunted so that by understanding those mindsets we can hope to detect other potential rapists

name: Ram Gopal Varma
text: Instead of impractical emotional outbursts of wanting to castrate them and burning them the concerned organisations should demand for a televised questioning of the rapists by psychiatrists and social scientists to understand what makes such people possible

name: Ram Gopal Varma
text: To barrier so that it can‚Äôt reach us or to kill it in cold blood or to cage it is the best way to deal with a dangerous snake ..To get angry with it will have no effect and just by cutting it to pieces the next snake won‚Äôt even know because it‚Äôs incapable of knowing and thinking

name: Ram Gopal Varma
text: In my tweets on Dr.Priyanka I dint mean that we should ignore the culprits like dogs ..The rapists should be treated like a disease and work in a scientific way to get them either out of the system or create safe environments to insulate vulnerable women from such attacks

name: Ram Gopal Varma
text: No rapist ever learns from the fate of earlier rapists and we saw this from before Nirbhaya in 2012 till now..That‚Äôs   because they will not have the mental capacity to learn and fear the same way as a mad dog cannot learn from what happened to another mad dog

name: Ram Gopal Varma
text: The sensitivity of Dr.Priyanka‚Äôs rapists will be lesser than wild dogs.Hence there‚Äôs no point in screaming for violent revenge..It‚Äôs point less to ask for brutal punishment for wild dogs ..instead effort should be on creating a sure safe atmosphere at vulnerable places for women.
